00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,700
Very well.

22
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:55,980
So it's like this.

23
00:01:59,630 --> 00:02:01,340
Talk.

24
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:04,210
You say it.

25
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:11,440
No, Third Brother. Don't be mad. We didn't hide it on purpose.

26
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:15,940
That's right. We saw that you liked her so much, so we wanted to help you.

27
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:19,340
Since her father wrote a letter, so we...

28
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:23,750
Yes, Third Brother. In the end, we did everything for your good.

29
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,260
Get out.

30
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:31,840
Third Brother, don't overthink it.

31
00:02:35,010 --> 00:02:38,520
Yes. Look at how many girls want to marry you in Beixin City.

32
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,910
Is Lin Hangjing blind? Then I—

33
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:42,640
Get out!

34
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,250
Let's go.

35
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:47,070
No, no. Third Brother, listen to me.

36
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:49,810
- Let's go.
- Third Brother.

37
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:02,800
He's drunk at Ming Yu Yue? Why are you still standing here?

38
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,420
Go and get him back.

39
00:03:04,420 --> 00:03:06,700
Master... Master is very drunk.

40
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:09,940
He said he doesn't want to cause a scene, so he's going to sleep there.

41
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:11,560
Hangjing.

42
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:15,810
Seventh Aunt, why are you still up so late?

43
00:03:15,810 --> 00:03:17,290
I'm waiting for Third Master.

44
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:21,300
This afternoon he went to Ming Yu Yue and now he's drunk. He doesn't want to come back.

45
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:24,880
Why is Third Master suddenly angry again?

46
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,080
Do you know what happened?

47
00:03:27,830 --> 00:03:31,990
I... I'm not sure.

48
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:36,290
Why are still standing here? Go to Ming Yu Yue and watch him.

49
00:03:36,290 --> 00:03:38,890
Don't let him drink more. Make him come back as soon as he sobers up.

50
00:03:38,890 --> 00:03:40,760
Yes, Seventh Madam.

51
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:49,310
Seventh Aunt, I'll go back. Go to bed early.

52
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:51,570
All right. Go ahead.

53
