♫ It's like decaying ruins ♫

54
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:15,950
[Warm Breeze from the South]

55
00:04:15,950 --> 00:04:23,510
♫ It's like decaying ruins ♫

56
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:32,790
♫ It's like decaying ruins ♫

57
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:35,510
Lanlan, won't you go and persuade him?

58
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:37,490
Can't you see his face?

59
00:04:37,490 --> 00:04:39,600
Scary. I don't dare.

60
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:42,590
You're such a useless brat.

61
00:04:42,590 --> 00:04:44,690
If you're so able, you go talk to him.

62
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:48,380
- I can't either. I'm even more timid than you.
- And you're talking about me.

63
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:54,510
♫ Happiness belongs to others ♫

64
00:04:54,510 --> 00:05:00,970
[Harmony in Prosperity]

65
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:33,450
Troupe Leader, what happened to Third Master?

66
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:35,440
I've never seen him drink so much.

67
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:40,700
Right, what matter has Third Master faced that he's so drunk?

68
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:45,380
Troupe Leader, I wish you were here earlier to persuade him.

69
00:05:46,490 --> 00:05:49,530
We need the one who started it to untie the knot.

70
00:05:49,530 --> 00:05:52,710
Unfortunately, none of us is that person.

71
00:05:52,710 --> 00:05:56,670
But we can't just have Third Master keep drinking like this.

72
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:13,170
Why is Chairman Sato from the Japanese Chamber of Commerce suddenly visiting us?

73
00:06:13,170 --> 00:06:16,790
We rarely have anything to do with the Japanese Chamber of Commerce.

74
00:06:18,130 --> 00:06:21,200
A visit from the Japanese can never be a good thing.

75
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:25,680
It's like a yellow weasel paying a visit to a chicken. They're up to no good!

76
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,000
You're right.

77
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:31,370
Commander, the Japanese first took over Taiwan and then occupied North Korea.

78
00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:35,120
And they took over all the privileges in Shandong from the Germans.

79
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:40,680
The Japanese Chamber of Commerce in China has a political background more or less. We should be careful.

80
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,070
That's right.

81
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:45,350
Eldest Brother, rest assured. We'll have our troops prepared for the enemy

82
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:48,580
and earth for a flood. If they dare offend us,

83
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:51,110
we'll teach them a lesson.

84
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:54,230
Look at this.

85
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:56,660
This Letter of Visit looks so ungenerous.

86
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:58,520
Exactly!

87
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:03,760
Okay. Let's listen to what they have to say first.

88
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,120
You two.

89
00:07:07,890 --> 00:07:13,510
Your third brother has not shown up in this East Camp for quite a few days. Where is he?

90
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,940
Reporting to Commander.

91
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:19,970
Third Brother has been busy with a social engagement these days.

92
00:07:19,970 --> 00:07:22,760
So he wants to get some rest for a few days.

93
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:26,650
Social engagement? You two just keep helping him

94
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:29,890
to lie to me. Social engagement?

95
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:35,060
Cheers!

96
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:37,270
Fill the glass!

97
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,270
Young Master Xu. Young Master Mo.

98
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:42,650
Sit down.

99
00:07:44,410 --> 00:07:46,860
What brings you here?

100
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:48,880
What are you doing here?

101
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,900
Get some glasses. Pour some wine for them!

102
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:53,180
Let's drink together!

103
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:55,620
Third Brother, stop drinking.

104
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:59,220
How many days have you been drinking? Do you want to drink yourself to death?

105
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:01,780
What are you talking about?

106
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:05,120
It's not like you haven't drunk like this with me.

107
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:08,990
Third Brother, here's the thing. Commander has been looking for you for quite a few days.

108
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:12,700
If you still don't go back, I can't explain it to him.

109
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:15,680
Why are you being so pretentious?

110
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,230
Acting like you're the boss.

111
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:21,260
- Cheers
- Cheers!

112
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:26,460
Third Brother! Please stop. Don't drink anymore.

113
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:30,500
Let go of me. There are so many people here. Nothing can go wrong.

114
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:33,850
Third Brother, last glass.

115
00:08:33,850 --> 00:08:35,970
Be quick, you two!

116
00:08:35,970 --> 00:08:37,340
- Let's drink!
- Come with me.

117
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:40,020
Cheers!

118
00:08:42,420 --> 00:08:43,710
What is it?

119
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:46,160
This is not going to work.

120
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,270
Let's leave here for now.

121
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,970
Cheers, Third Brother!

122
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:50,350
Come on.

123
00:08:50,970 --> 00:08:53,780
We brothers must drink this one!

124
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:15,150
Xiao Rong!

125
00:09:17,410 --> 00:09:19,670
Why are you hiding from me?

126
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,940
Seventh Madam, good day.

127
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:26,640
I asked you to bring Third Master back. Where is he?

128
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:30,470
- Well...
- What's happening? Tell me the truth!

129
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:33,740
Seventh Madam, actually... it's nothing serious.

130
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:37,360
Even if I had 100 guts, I wouldn't dare lie to you.

131
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:39,630
Do you think I have no idea what you're thinking?

132
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:43,060
Tell me exactly what's happening!

133
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:44,360
Well...

134
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:48,550
Young Master will strip my skin if I do!

135
00:09:49,370 --> 00:09:51,420
You're not telling me?

136
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:55,120
- I will strip your skin right now!
- Fine, fine! I'll say it!

137
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,790
A few days ago, Young Master was waiting for Miss Lin

138
00:09:57,790 --> 00:10:00,090
for quite a few hours in the park.

139
00:10:00,090 --> 00:10:03,670
But Miss Lin didn't show up. So Young Master went looking for her.

140
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:07,110
But on his way back...

141
00:10:08,950 --> 00:10:10,550
Miss Lin.

142
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:18,730
Miss Lin, Xiao Rong told us about everything between you and Third Brother.

143
00:10:18,730 --> 00:10:22,630
We're here to apologize to you.

144
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:26,200
Miss Lin, we're very sorry about what we did that year.

145
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:29,790
It was all your fault! That was a terrible idea.

146
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,500
My idea?

147
00:10:33,250 --> 00:10:37,310
Yes, it was all my fault. So blame it all on me.

148
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:44,350
Miss Lin, this time we're asking you to come to Ming Yu Yue, to persuade Third Brother.

149
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:50,380
This is really not something I can interfere in.

150
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:53,360
You... please don't say that, Miss Lin. If you can't handle it, who else can?

151
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:57,700
If you still don't do anything about it, I'm afraid Third Brother will die from drinking in Ming Yu Yue.

152
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:59,230
It's true.

153
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,720
Lin Hangjing!

154
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:12,510
[Tu Chin Sheng Silk Weaving Factory]

155
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:15,580
What we'd done before was indeed wrong.

156
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:18,900
We sincerely apologize to you about it here.

157
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:29,670
But Third Brother's affection for you is real.

158
00:11:31,570 --> 00:11:35,310
Do you know how he got through these years?

159
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:40,660
Third Brother hated war since he was a child.

160
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:43,330
The reason why he went to military school...

161
00:11:43,330 --> 00:11:45,990
Do you really think Commander was able to convince him?

162
00:11:45,990 --> 00:11:48,980
If it's something Third Brother doesn't want to do, then in the whole of Beixin City,

163
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:51,830
no one can force him.

164
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:55,830
The reason he went there was that you said he was useless.

165
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:58,310
That he was living under the protection of Commander.

166
00:11:58,310 --> 00:12:00,620
So he went without hesitation.

167
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:04,460
He wanted to prove to you that he was a real man.

168
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:07,130
He wants to be the hero in your heart.

169
00:12:07,130 --> 00:12:10,510
When he was at the military school, he trained day and night.

170
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:12,670
He was wounded everywhere on his body.

171
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:17,050
Do you know how he managed to get through it?

172
00:12:18,930 --> 00:12:20,650
I don't know how many times,

173
00:12:20,650 --> 00:12:24,350
when I woke up in the dormitory at night,

174
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:27,830
I saw him holding the book you gave him,

175
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:32,260
just as if it was the best comfort in the world.

176
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:37,360
For the Feng City war, others only know that he won an admirable victory, despite having fewer soldiers.

177
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:39,950
But he was hit by a bullet on his left shoulder and was bleeding heavily.

178
00:12:39,950 --> 00:12:42,770
He almost died.

179
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:45,770
He needed surgery to get the bullet out.

180
00:12:45,770 --> 00:12:47,720
But there were no anesthetics.

181
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:51,420
He just bore with the whole process with clenched teeth.

182
00:12:52,330 --> 00:12:55,120
Because he knew you were waiting for him at home.

183
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,570
He couldn't just die.

184
00:12:57,570 --> 00:13:01,120
He wanted to finish the war as soon as possible and come back home to see you.

185
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:06,980
Miss Lin, do you still remember the Russian Doll he gave you?

186
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:09,370
It wasn't some item at a stall.

187
00:13:09,370 --> 00:13:11,300
It was something that he crafted for you by hand.

188
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:14,430
He saw that a lot of girls in Russia liked them.

189
00:13:14,430 --> 00:13:16,920
So he wanted to make one for you.

190
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:19,420
Do you know how many times he had failed?

191
00:13:19,420 --> 00:13:23,540
And how many cuts he had on his hands? He's even got scars on his hands now.

192
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:28,230
Miss Lin.

193
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:30,800
You have a right to not like him.

194
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:35,320
But once people fall in love, it's hard to take it back.

195
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:39,770
Third Brother's affection for you has grown day by day.

196
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:43,170
So he can't just let it go easily.

197
00:13:43,170 --> 00:13:47,330
And now, you're the only one

198
00:13:47,330 --> 00:13:50,040
that can untie the knot for him.

199
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:54,900
We've told you everything you need to know.

200
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:59,280
It's up to you whether you will go or not.

201
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,670
I...

202
00:14:19,760 --> 00:14:21,180
Tell me about it now.

203
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:23,730
Third Master has not been back for quite a few days!

204
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:26,970
He's been staying at Ming Yu Yue, right?

205
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:30,740
How old is he? It's normal that he would go out and have a drink.

206
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:33,460
And... maybe he has some serious topics to discuss.

207
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:35,910
You're just helping him hide the truth!

208
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:39,940
He hasn't shown up in East Camp for quite a few days! What would his subordinates think?

209
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:42,650
It's okay, it's okay. Don't be angry.

210
00:14:42,650 --> 00:14:46,260
Third Master has been at East Camp ever since he came back. Let him rest.

211
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:48,580
They have their own ideas. We as elders

212
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:50,900
should give them some freedom.

213
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:53,410
I'll just have him come back.

214
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,820
What a worrisome kid.

215
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:03,060
Bottoms up!

216
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:06,180
Third Master! Third Master!

217
00:15:20,190 --> 00:15:22,380
Another round!

218
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:25,980
[Ming Yu Yue]

219
00:15:38,820 --> 00:15:41,550
[Ming Yu Yue]

220
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:01,160
Cheers!

221
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,780
Drink it all!

222
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:05,880
One more!

223
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:08,200
- Let's drink!
- This is good wine!

224
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:10,050
Let's drink!

225
00:16:10,050 --> 00:16:13,420
Fill the glass!

226
00:16:13,420 --> 00:16:14,940
Third Brother!

227
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:17,140
Third Brother!

228
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:33,260
I drank it up.

229
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:35,810
It's your turn!

230
00:16:35,810 --> 00:16:37,780
No problem!

231
00:16:37,780 --> 00:16:39,630
One more!

232
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:43,290
Stop drinking, Third Brother. Come home with me.

233
00:16:46,010 --> 00:16:47,920
Third Brother, who is she?

234
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:50,470
How dare she stop you from drinking?

235
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:55,280
Isn't this Lin Hangjing, Eldest Miss Lin?

236
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:57,380
Lin Hangjing?

237
00:16:57,380 --> 00:17:00,170
The girl who's residing in the Xiao Family.

238
00:17:00,170 --> 00:17:03,480
She's not that good-looking.

239
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:12,840
Miss Lin, why don't you drink with me?

240
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:17,300
That Miss Lin.

241
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:19,500
- Third Brother!
- Be careful, Third Brother.

242
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:21,610
She's not going to be interested

243
00:17:21,610 --> 00:17:23,810
in ordinary guys like you.

244
00:17:23,810 --> 00:17:27,050
The No.1 talented girl in Yulin!

245
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:29,350
Now,

246
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:32,560
in Beixin, she is probably

247
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:35,450
the most pure and noble...

248
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:38,680
What are you doing?

249
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,710
Have you woken up?

250
00:17:40,710 --> 00:17:43,970
Be quiet! Disperse!

251
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:45,420
Let's go.

252
00:17:59,110 --> 00:18:02,960
[Time Passes Like Sand]

253
00:18:05,850 --> 00:18:08,040
Why are you here?

254
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:10,530
When will you stop drinking?

255
00:18:11,620 --> 00:18:14,910
I can do whatever I want.

256
00:18:14,910 --> 00:18:20,360
I can drink whenever I want.

257
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:24,610
Why do you care? What right do you have...

258
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:29,450
Yes. I indeed don't have the right to care.

259
00:18:29,450 --> 00:18:34,740
But you're ruining yourself. It only makes Uncle Xiao and Seventh Aunt worry about you more.

260
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:38,940
Now you're worried about me?

261
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:43,890
Aren't you supposed to be with your kite lover now?

262
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:52,290
Third Brother, Mo Weiyi told me all about it.

263
00:18:53,130 --> 00:18:57,950
