264
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:02,140
But...

265
00:19:05,890 --> 00:19:07,830
But what?

266
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:12,370
But you can't like me?

267
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:20,810
Lin Hangjing, are you so happy to learn about

268
00:19:20,810 --> 00:19:23,220
