269
00:19:28,700 --> 00:19:31,460
You don't need to be here.

270
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:35,570
You're just here to watch me, to make fun of me.

271
00:19:35,570 --> 00:19:39,520
Third Brother, I'm not making fun of you.

272
00:19:40,340 --> 00:19:43,570
If I had done anything that misled you,

273
00:19:43,570 --> 00:19:48,260
I'm sorry. Since I've been in this family,

274
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:51,660
I always thought you hated me and you were teasing me.

275
00:19:51,660 --> 00:19:54,250
I never thought that one day you'd...

276
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:04,300
All these years, the only thing I've been thinking about

277
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:07,010
is reuniting with my father.

278
00:20:07,010 --> 00:20:10,280
I‘m going to leave Beixin one day.

279
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:14,360
How can I be so fortunate to deserve everything you've done?

280
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:20,510
Third Brother, I really appreciate the care the Xiao Family has been giving me all these years.

281
00:20:20,510 --> 00:20:23,210
I think of you as my family.

282
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:25,960
You're just like my family with a bond of blood.

283
00:20:27,950 --> 00:20:30,500
So you like someone else?

284
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:35,500
Love has to be mutual.

285
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:38,990
Lin Hangjing.

286
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:45,460
I'm telling you. Across Beixin, I, Xiao Beichen,

287
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:47,990
for everything I want,

288
00:20:48,870 --> 00:20:50,950
I never fail to get it.

289
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:53,810
I'm not an item for you to play with.

290
00:20:53,810 --> 00:20:55,980
I have the right to make my own decisions.

291
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:58,200
Nobody can force me to do anything.

292
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:00,570
Force you to do what?

293
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,450
Let go of me!

294
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:12,240
Xiao Beichen, what are you doing?

295
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,780
Lady.

296
00:22:23,910 --> 00:22:27,580
Lady, your eyes are red.

297
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:29,710
Did you just cry?

298
00:22:29,710 --> 00:22:31,570
I didn't.

299
00:22:32,330 --> 00:22:35,660
Did someone bully you? I'm going to tell Seventh Madam.

300
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:37,520
It's fine.

301
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:39,770
Please tell Seventh Madam that

302
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:42,890
there's no need to prepare my dinner. I want to rest a bit.

303
00:22:42,890 --> 00:22:45,900
But... Lady...

