[Harmony in Prosperity]

305
00:23:07,410 --> 00:23:10,620
If I had done anything that misled you,

306
00:23:10,620 --> 00:23:12,790
I'm sorry.

307
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:16,110
I really appreciate the care Xiao Family has been giving me all these years.

308
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:18,850
I think of you as my family.

309
00:23:18,850 --> 00:23:21,240
You're just like my family with a bond of blood.

310
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:23,880
So you like someone else?

311
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:27,020
Love has to be mutual.

312
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,610
Father,

313
00:23:43,610 --> 00:23:46,760
your skill is getting better and better.

314
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:49,700
I still remember you cutting my hair when I was young.

315
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:53,330
My head looked like a watermelon.

316
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,880
I'm telling you,

317
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:58,380
I heard from the elders in the family say,

318
00:23:58,380 --> 00:24:01,830
"If the father cuts the son's hair, it can get rid of ominous luck.

319
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:05,400
It can also allow the son to grow up healthily."

320
00:24:06,050 --> 00:24:09,450
That's why you went to Dongjiao Alley to learn this skill?

321
00:24:09,450 --> 00:24:14,480
Do you know how jealous Beichen and Zijun were when they were young?

322
00:24:15,530 --> 00:24:20,190
Speaking of which, how come I haven't seen Beichen these last couple of days?

323
00:24:20,190 --> 00:24:22,620
There's so much talk in the army.

324
00:24:22,620 --> 00:24:25,020
What happened to him?

325
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:30,710
That's Third Brother's personal matter, you don't need to be worried.

326
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:34,650
Fine.

327
00:24:37,070 --> 00:24:41,640
You're now grown men, you hate us nagging, don't you?

328
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:44,430
Fine. You better find that white Russian barber.

329
00:24:44,430 --> 00:24:48,150
I don't want that, Dad. I want you to cut my hair.

330
00:24:48,150 --> 00:24:52,380
Also, this is your love for me, isn't it?

331
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:58,670
You brat! Sit tight.

