00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:11,450
[Music in Heyday]

334
00:25:45,260 --> 00:25:49,610
How come Third Brother hasn't been here to play with us in the last few days?

335
00:25:49,610 --> 00:25:52,410
Your third brother is so busy, he doesn't have time to always play with you two.

336
00:25:52,410 --> 00:25:55,220
What is he busy with? Busy with fooling around?

337
00:25:55,220 --> 00:25:58,110
Stop the nonsense. That's a business event.

338
00:25:58,110 --> 00:26:00,920
What business event? I heard

