00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:03,350
he has been drinking at Ming Yu Yue.

340
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,530
He has been so drunk.

341
00:26:05,530 --> 00:26:09,170
But why is he drinking to that extent?

342
00:26:14,950 --> 00:26:19,280
No. I need to go find him. I can't let him carry on drinking.

343
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:22,330
Third Master is here.

344
00:26:22,330 --> 00:26:25,500
- Third Master is here.
- Third Brother, you're here.

345
00:26:25,500 --> 00:26:26,840
- Beichen.
- Third Master.

346
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:29,060
Beichen, are you okay?

347
00:26:29,060 --> 00:26:31,850
I'm sorry to make you worry, Seventh Aunt.

348
00:26:33,290 --> 00:26:37,190
Third Brother! Why haven't you come home to sleep these past few days?

349
00:26:37,190 --> 00:26:40,870
- Beiwang misses you.
- Beiyi also misses you.

350
00:26:40,870 --> 00:26:45,480
My mother also misses you. Sister Shuyi also misses you.

351
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:48,940
Also, Sister Hangjing misses you a lot, too.

352
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:52,440
I miss you guys, too.

353
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:55,880
Beichen, perfect timing. Have some food.

354
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:58,300
No, Seventh Aunt. I need to handle something in my study.

355
00:26:58,300 --> 00:26:59,950
I'll get going.

356
00:26:59,950 --> 00:27:03,290
You don't want to eat? Later, I'll have Xiao Rong to bring you some bird's nest soup.

357
00:27:03,290 --> 00:27:05,160
Got it, Seventh Madam.

