00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:52,400
[The Whole River Red by Yue Fei]

378
00:29:59,870 --> 00:30:01,650
Commander!

379
00:30:10,360 --> 00:30:12,630
Commander Xiao. My name is Yoshida.

380
00:30:12,630 --> 00:30:16,390
This one is the head of the Japanese Chamber of Commerce, Director Sato.

381
00:30:19,330 --> 00:30:22,790
I've been hearing Commander Xiao is a combative leader, heroic, and majestic.

382
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:26,850
Now that I see you in person, it's indeed carrying this inordinary demeanor.

383
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,880
Have a seat.

384
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:50,160
Commander Xiao, as a talented leader,

385
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:54,290
I've been admiring you for a long time, and I should've visited you a long time ago.

386
00:30:54,290 --> 00:30:58,100
Unfortunately, I have a lot of work engagements. I hope you understand.

387
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:01,470
You don't need to be courteous.

388
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:07,100
I always welcome friendly businessmen from different countries.

389
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:26,020
This medal is a gift from our chamber of commerce.

390
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:29,620
It represents our good intentions. I hope you will accept it.

391
00:31:30,850 --> 00:31:33,000
I'm sorry you need to spend money on this.

392
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:35,020
You've spoken too seriously.

393
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:42,930
The brush moved like a dragon and snake, the strokes were strong and powerful.

394
00:31:42,930 --> 00:31:45,440
It's amazing penmanship.

395
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:48,840
That was a piece of calligraphy I did a few years ago;

396
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:51,660
it's nothing amazing.

397
00:31:51,660 --> 00:31:54,100
Commander, you're overly humble.

398
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:56,510
I have an unreasonable request.

399
00:31:56,510 --> 00:32:01,270
It'll be an honor to have a piece of your work.

400
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:04,400
I've been busy on the battlefield,

401
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:07,090
I'm no longer practicing calligraphy.

402
00:32:07,090 --> 00:32:10,080
Commander, this is my first visit.

403
00:32:10,080 --> 00:32:12,200
If you reject my request,

404
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:15,410
it's because you're looking down on me.

405
00:32:15,410 --> 00:32:18,060
I'm hoping Commander can offer your piece of art;

406
00:32:18,060 --> 00:32:21,510
otherwise, this visit will become an unproductive trip.

407
00:32:33,950 --> 00:32:35,380
Commander!

408
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:47,760
You must be the son of Commander Xiao,

409
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:50,240
Beixin City Third Master Xiao.

410
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:53,840
I'm Maruro Sato from the Japanese Chamber of Commerce.

411
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:55,650
Nice to meet you.

412
00:32:56,580 --> 00:32:57,970
Director Sato.

413
00:32:57,970 --> 00:33:01,930
I wonder what the purpose of your visit is?

414
00:33:01,930 --> 00:33:04,460
Mainly it's to come here to visit Commander Xiao.

415
00:33:04,460 --> 00:33:08,470
I'm lucky to see his calligraphy work and wanted to add it to my collection.

416
00:33:08,470 --> 00:33:11,930
So that I could enjoy it in the future.

417
00:33:13,850 --> 00:33:17,430
How about this? My father's hand has a little bit of a problem.

418
00:33:17,430 --> 00:33:19,590
He can't write right now.

419
00:33:21,210 --> 00:33:24,620
Commander, why didn't you tell me earlier?

420
00:33:24,620 --> 00:33:27,700
It's an old problem, nothing serious.

421
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:31,780
Since it's like this, on behalf of my father,

422
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:34,580
would you accept my penmanship instead?

423
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:36,280
Of course.

424
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:40,390
We'd be very happy with Third Master's work.

425
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:48,180
[Flying high ...]

426
00:33:56,580 --> 00:33:59,280
[Dark...]

427
00:34:16,370 --> 00:34:21,230
[Waves splashed high]

428
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:42,000
[Cloud moves in the dark sky, waves splash high]
(T/N: It's the scenery of a gathering storm)

429
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:46,450
Director Sato, those powerful words suit you very well.

430
00:34:46,450 --> 00:34:48,260
I hope you like it.

431
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:52,300
Third Master's work is as good as Commander's.

432
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:58,070
- You're too kind.
- But something is missing.

433
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:00,340
What's missing?

434
00:35:00,340 --> 00:35:05,120
I remember those lines should be, "Clouds move in the black sky,

435
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:08,150
waves splash high."

436
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:13,550
I really didn't expect Director Sato

437
00:35:13,550 --> 00:35:16,920
had deep understanding of Chinese culture.

438
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:19,140
Third Master, thanks for the kind words.

439
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:22,480
Chinese culture is broad and profound,

440
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:26,000
I only know a small part of it.

441
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:28,130
That's right.

442
00:35:28,130 --> 00:35:33,030
Those lines were supposed to be that way. I'm not mistaken.

443
00:35:33,950 --> 00:35:35,600
Of course.

444
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:40,400
Third Master didn't make any mistake, the mistake is mine.

445
00:35:45,290 --> 00:35:47,740
Thank you, Third Master, for your calligraphy.

446
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:51,540
Commander. Third Master. I've taken up too much of your time.

447
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:52,940
We're heading out now.

448
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:54,310
Deputy Officer Guo, please see them out.

449
00:35:54,310 --> 00:35:55,940
Yes, Sir!

450
00:36:04,530 --> 00:36:06,870
I don't think these two come here with kindness.

451
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:09,890
You, kiddo, know your way home?

452
00:36:09,890 --> 00:36:13,930
What's the matter? You don't think I came here at the right time?

453
00:36:13,930 --> 00:36:15,940
It's the perfect time.

454
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:22,150
[The Army of Frontier Command for Zhibei Region]

455
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:50,550
If we publish the calligraphy gifted by the Xiao Family,

456
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:53,470
it'll be like we'd be telling the world

457
00:36:53,470 --> 00:36:55,340
the Xiao Family is friendly with us.

458
00:36:55,340 --> 00:37:00,190
Then it'll be a lot easier for us to do business in Beixin.

459
00:37:05,040 --> 00:37:07,190
Director, what are you doing?

460
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,820
You want to plot against the others?

461
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:12,310
They have already set you up.

462
00:37:12,310 --> 00:37:15,230
If we publish the calligraphy in the paper,

463
00:37:15,230 --> 00:37:18,350
it'll be a deadly humiliation for our emperor.

464
00:37:18,350 --> 00:37:21,800
I don't understand.

465
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:24,690
Xiao Beichen made it clear to us that

466
00:37:24,690 --> 00:37:26,730
they won't give an inch to us.

467
00:37:26,730 --> 00:37:30,520
There will be no profits for us at all.

468
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:32,790
Not giving us an inch?

469
00:37:32,790 --> 00:37:36,160
I don't get it.

470
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:39,150
It's for you to take it home and figure it out.

471
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:44,020
Nevertheless, he and his father are not easy to deal with.

472
00:37:47,060 --> 00:37:50,440
But Beixin is an unavoidable transit stop for this batch of goods.

473
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,420
If they don't approve, then...

474
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:56,230
We have time. There is no need to worry now.

475
00:37:56,990 --> 00:38:02,360
Xiao has refused to work with us, but it will not stop us from looking for other means.

476
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:05,720
You don't need to worry.

477
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:08,260
Wording matters are like chess.

478
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:12,390
Sometimes you are against a competent opponent.

479
00:38:12,390 --> 00:38:15,570
But that's what it takes to have a good game.

480
00:38:15,570 --> 00:38:17,220
It's your call.

481
00:38:25,010 --> 00:38:26,920
Third Brother.

482
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:30,950
Little brother, what are you doing here?

483
00:38:30,950 --> 00:38:35,130
I can't sleep. Can you read a story for me?

484
00:38:35,130 --> 00:38:38,290
It's late, you cheeky boy.

485
00:38:38,290 --> 00:38:39,770
Come on. Go back to your room and sleep.

486
00:38:39,770 --> 00:38:43,980
Third Brother, can we go horse riding tomorrow?

487
00:38:48,690 --> 00:38:50,600
Well,

488
00:38:53,230 --> 00:38:55,330
I'm busy tomorrow.

489
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:58,330
Then let's go to Huaxin Hotel to have seafood.

490
00:38:58,330 --> 00:39:00,960
I heard they have a new cook.

491
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:03,260
You cheeky boy.

492
00:39:03,260 --> 00:39:05,220
How did you know about that?

493
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:09,220
But I have been really busy lately.

494
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:12,010
I will take you out when I have time.

495
00:39:12,010 --> 00:39:14,990
Have you...

496
00:39:14,990 --> 00:39:18,890
had a fight with Sister Hangjing?

497
00:39:24,370 --> 00:39:28,330
A child shouldn't interfere with adult matters.

498
00:39:28,330 --> 00:39:31,440
It's been a long time since we last slept together.

499
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:33,450
Can I sleep here today?

500
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,920
Hey!

501
00:39:40,290 --> 00:39:43,810
You cheeky boy. You are quick to get into my bed.

502
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:49,090
Come on. Which story do you want to listen to?

503
00:39:49,090 --> 00:39:50,730
This one.

504
00:39:51,580 --> 00:39:54,000
There is a man called Pang Tong.

505
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,090
He came to Feng Wei Hills one day.

506
00:39:56,090 --> 00:39:57,780
Then...

507
00:40:00,190 --> 00:40:04,970
Commander Kang, I have an urgent matter for that I may need your help with.

508
00:40:06,310 --> 00:40:08,680
Mr. Sato, there's no need for such formality.

509
00:40:08,680 --> 00:40:12,480
We've been in partnership for three years.

510
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:15,770
If you're in trouble,

511
00:40:15,770 --> 00:40:18,270
